Package: ggSynteny
Type: Package
Title: Genome Synteny Data Processing and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Author: Jiawang1209 [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jiawang1209 <Jiawang1209@163.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Jiawang1209",
      email = "Jiawang1209@163.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Tools for preparing pairwise genome synteny data and
    drawing genome-level and micro-synteny visualizations in R.
    The package currently supports MCScanX and jcvi-style pairwise
    inputs, optional GFF3 annotation enrichment, and transcript-aware
    local gene structure plotting.
